    "date_str": "2025-09-25",
    "description": "Zakath and poverty: Why the powerful tool falls short in Sri Lanka",
    "url_metadata": "https://www.ft.lk/columns/Zakath-and-poverty-Why-the-powerful-tool-falls-short-in-Sri-Lanka/4-782124",
    "lang": "en",
    "newspaper_id": "dailyftlk",
